title: HUMAN EVENTS DAILY: DEC 14 2021 - GHISLAINE MAXWELL TO CALL 35 WITNESSES TO THE STAND
description:
Ghislaine Maxwell is set to call 35 witnesses to the stand for her defense, Facebook admits in court that ‘Fact Checks’ are just opinions, EA suspends Kyle Rittenhouse’s account - for using his own name, and Waukesha feels abandoned after a tragic parade attack.


Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
